    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188810/extras/a40977682e729c152eaa03cae5351188.avif?t=1727110931\" width=462 height=174 /></span><br><br><i>Powerful plants fight off invading weeds in a wacky 2D tower-defense game with Roguelite elements!</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2>~ Casual but challenging tower defense gameplay! Build up your plant-based defenses to fend off the invading weeds.<br>~ 4 different friend and foe types with unique stats and abilities!<br>~ Endlessly replayable. Upgrade your defenses, power up your plant army, or add another Bumble-Buzz to your meadow to boost your pollen production!<br>~ Easy to pick up, hard to master. Hyper-casual gameplay to kill time!<br>~ Roguelite elements! Use your upgrade cards to specialize your plant army, complete your run, complete challenges... then try again and build up a whole new loadout!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HOW TO PLAY:</strong></h2>~ Select a plant in the top left, then tap where you want place it in the meadow.<br>~ Use your different plants to fight against the incoming waves of increasingly-powerful weeds.<br>~ At the end of each round, select a reward card to power up your plant army!<br>~ Will you focus on attack? Defense? Or pollen production?<br>~ Complete challenges to build up your deck in the Card Bank!<br>~ Survive as many waves as you can - then try again to see if you can survive longer!<br><br><br>PLANTOONS is an indie game created by Theo Clarke and Chloe Page of the 2D Game Jammers Discord Community!",
